<emphasis box="[1007,1240,253,275]" italics="true" pageId="108" pageNumber="109">Falklandiella annulata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Hartman" box="[1246,1400,253,275]" pageId="108" pageNumber="109" refString="Hartman, O. (1967) Polychaetous annelids collected by the USNS Eltanin and Staten Island cruises, chiefly from Antarctic seas. Allan Hancock Monographs in Marine Biology, 2, 1 - 387, 51 plates." type="book chapter" year="1967">Hartman, 1967</bibRefCitation>
